      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>You're always ready for a tussle or twelve. When an attack succeeds against your AC, you can use your reaction to increase your AC as though you were @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#fight-defensively]{fighting defensively}; if you also spend 1 Resolve Point, calculate your AC as though you were using the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#total-defense]{total defense} action instead. This can change a successful hit into a miss. Either way, you remain fighting defensively or totally defending yourself until the start of your next turn.</p>"
